---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — xCrypto24" description="How xCrypto24 handles your data. We collect minimal analytics, store coin data in your browser, and never access your wallet or keys." keywords="xcrypto24 privacy, crypto tracker privacy policy, data protection, GDPR">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebPage","name":"Privacy Policy","url":"https://xcrypto24.com/privacy","description":"How xCrypto24 handles your data, cookies, and analytics."})} />
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem;">At xCrypto24.com, your privacy is fundamental. This policy explains what data we collect, why, and how you control it. We are a crypto tracking tool — we do not hold your funds, keys, or personal financial data.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">1. Information We Collect</h2>

    <div style="margin:1.5rem 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1rem;">
      <div style="padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(88,28,135,0.15);">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;"><span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:600;">Anonymous Analytics:</span> Page views, country (region-level), device type, browser. No personally identifiable information.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(88,28,135,0.15);">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;"><span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:600;">LocalStorage (your browser only):</span> User ID (random UUID), filter preferences, theme, scan history, update logs. Never sent to our servers.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(88,28,135,0.15);">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;"><span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:600;">Database (our servers):</span> Coin tracking data you explicitly add (coin names, contract addresses, DexScreener URLs). Linked to your anonymous User ID only.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(88,28,135,0.15);">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;"><span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:600;">Contact Form:</span> If you contact us, we store your name, email, and message to respond.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">2. What We Do NOT Collect</h2>

    <div style="margin:1.5rem 0;padding:1.2rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3);background:rgba(20,83,45,0.1);">
      <p style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:#4ade80;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">✓ We Never Collect</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;">Wallet addresses, private keys, seed phrases, transaction history, financial balances, passwords, or any data that could access your cryptocurrency. We are a read-only tracker — not a wallet or exchange.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">We use the following third-party APIs to provide real-time data:</p>
    <div style="margin:1.5rem 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0.75rem;">
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;"><strong style="color:#a78bfa;">DexScreener</strong> — token price and pair data</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;"><strong style="color:#a78bfa;">RugCheck.xyz</strong> — token safety analysis</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;"><strong style="color:#a78bfa;">Bubblemaps</strong> — holder distribution visualisation</p></div>
    </div>
    <p style="color:#a1a1aa;font-size:0.85rem;">These services have their own privacy policies. We send only public blockchain data (contract addresses) to them — never your personal information.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">4. Cookies</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">We use minimal cookies for analytics only. You can disable cookies in your browser settings without affecting the core functionality of the tracker.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <div style="margin:1.5rem 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0.75rem;">
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Clear localStorage at any time to remove all local preferences</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Request deletion of your tracked coins by contacting us</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Opt out of analytics by using browser ad-blockers</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">6. Contact</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;">For privacy inquiries, use our <a href="/contact" style="color:#c084fc;">contact form</a>.</p>

    <div style="margin-top:2rem;text-align:center;">
      <a href="/" style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.85rem;text-decoration:none;">← Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
